item.title: Imaginary CTF 2024
item.description: Overview ImaginaryCTF 2024 is a cybersecurity CTF competition run by ImaginaryCTF with a variety of challenges for all skill levels. It was started from July 20 to July 22, starting and ending at 12 AM GMT+5:45. For more information, check out last year’s challenges from ImaginaryCTF 2023, with over 2000 participants.
